dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Lincoln_Roads_2012.gdb.[This data set consists of digital map files containing road centerline information obtained predominantly by conducting field work using GPS technology. Features contained in the data set include all road centerlines countywide and associated attributes and annotation. The Lincoln County Land Information Office plans to maintain this digital data in geodatabase format in an ESRI ArcSDE environment using ArcMap tools.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
